{"tid":2102742,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"我相信香港人一定會assemble","createTime":"2020-07-10T16:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-10T20:23:01.000Z","uid":5205,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"46af69684013245da1f3123d411707fb922dd50d","tid":2102742,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:43:22.000Z","msg":"我相信香港人一定會assemble"},{"pid":"61dbe934aae281b953ff2dad1f6fa25c3e2a93aa","tid":2102742,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:51:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440de571d10249778002ced2902e540236619204","tid":2102742,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:58:55.000Z","msg":"睇下點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61746168900a63ca70a76ddcfed3a0756ccebfe0","tid":2102742,"uid":225542,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f160THJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff160THJ.png&h=3845cd03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可細閱後選人資料 <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hkfactcheck.io/posts/318029346266274\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhkfactcheck.io%2Fposts%2F318029346266274&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumrnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=09246ee3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hkfactcheck.io/posts/318029346266274</a>"},{"pid":"4d30943574f9d27c904ee72083c07f9ef9d9f431","tid":2102742,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"46af69684013245da1f3123d411707fb922dd50d","tid":2102742,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T16:43:22.000Z","msg":"我相信香港人一定會assemble"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-10T20:23:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PowerForDemocracy/photos/a.808713395853924/3191030574288849/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPowerForDemocracy%2Fphotos%2Fa.808713395853924%2F3191030574288849%2F&d=Wd2ZpPw6abVmqVF%2BhWwumrnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=f38441bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/PowerForDemocracy/photos/a.808713395853924/3191030574288849/</a><br />\n<br />\n【民主派35+公民投票 (初選)】#重要訊息 #請廣傳 : #服務站開放時間須延後至中午十二時！<br />\n<br />\n警方於7月10日晚，突進入 #香港民意研究所 對其電腦系統進行調查，導致#民主派初選 的最後階段準備工作被延誤。<br />\n<br />\n在此重申，初選所使用的是另一獨立電腦系統，警方的調查並不會影響於7月11日至7月12日進行的民主派初選。<br />\n<br />\n#民主動力 及兩位初選協調人獲悉香港民意研究所團隊的工作日程被打亂，亦以防萬一，<span class=\"gold\">技術團隊因系統安全考慮，正為系統重設加密匙。因此，#7月11日所有服務站的開放時間須延後至中午十二時正，敬請留意！</span><br />\n<br />\n同時，<span class=\"red\">Android 使用者將不能使用手機應用程式投票，投票方式將採用投票網頁進行投票。而IOS使用者則不受影響，依舊採用投票網頁進行投票。</span><br />\n<br />\n因此做成的不便，我們謹向廣大市民致歉。望所有投票的市民，能多多包容及忍耐。<br />\n<br />\n在惡法橫行的時代，我們要繼續不畏強權，以公民投票去拒絕謊言。提提大家，投票時除展示身份證外，須攜帶：✅過往的投票通知書 或 ✅住址證明 (文本、電子版本、截圖及相片皆接納)。<br />\n<br />\n#民主派 #35plus #公民投票 #初選<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<p class=\"right\">[重要！] 聽日7月11號  12點先開票站<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2102850\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2102850</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</p>"}]}